<p>This will also help us identify businesses that currently move goods between Great Britain and Northern Ireland.</p>

<h2 id="before-you-start">Before you start</h2>

<p>If your browser is an older one (for example, Internet Explorer 8) you’ll need to update it to a <a href="https://www.gov.uk/help/browsers" class="govuk-link">different browser</a> before you can complete the form.</p>

<p>You’ll need to fill in the form on screen. You cannot save a partly completed form, so have all the information you need before you start to fill it in.</p>

